ta-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n袋住先 放風降溫<br />\n大追捕 清算 正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"94fc10d14d56177f69a5c229261e51a53fb24a39","tid":1539400,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2cbc4de8f0c63a24fe5ee3d2950b1024f7184cac","tid":1539400,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:58:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d7867980287922f42f3806253bcb99d11dfbfeb0","tid":1539400,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:00:00.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a02f8760d7739df116d0829f0f6e8c8362607986","tid":1539400,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:01:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e5c5fbf59037e7dc79ec8eec42a0749ae133906a","tid":1539400,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2e7fd1fcc15e2661702f13ebdffe0817c43d0c99","tid":1539400,"uid":261095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"徹回條例想平息國際輿論？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539689</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9975f6cb4f4e00f43ec483610a3f86e419f498c2","tid":1539400,"uid":277743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:36:09.000Z","msg":"908 一定要出"},{"pid":"435680742db021f034e2d9c5e2c271dd7bcce998","tid":1539400,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply